folder: means the folder of origin from the query
db: means the database of the result
contig_count: means number of results for this contig with less identity
nt_db_seq: means nucleotide full sequence from db
aa_db_seq: means amino-acid full sequence from db
nt_db_longest_orf: means longest nucleotide orf from db in alignment
nt_db_longest_orf_len: means length of longest nucleotide orf from db in alignment
nt_db_longest_orf_same_size: means how many same sized longest nucleotide orf from db in alignment
aa_db_longest_orf: means longest amino-acid orf from db in alignment
aa_db_longest_orf_len: means length of longest amino-acid orf from db in alignment
aa_db_longest_orf_same_size: means how many same sized longest amino-acid orf from db in alignment
